metadata.startup-script:
CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      BOUNDARY_IP=$(gcloud compute instances describe boundary-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      mkdir -p /home/consul/data
      consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data -bind=$BOUNDARY_IP > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
      sudo mkdir /home/packer | cd /home/packer
      sudo touch init.txt
      IP_ADDR=$(gcloud compute instances describe boundary-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].accessConfigs[0].natIP)')
      sudo boundary dev  -api-listen-address 0.0.0.0:9200  -cluster-listen-address 0.0.0.0:9201 -proxy-listen-address=0.0.0.0:9202 -worker-public-address=$IP_ADDR > /dev/null 2>&1 &

CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      MYSQL_IP=$(gcloud compute instances describe mysql-db-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      mkdir -p /home/consul/data
      consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data -bind=$MYSQL_IP > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
      sudo systemctl start mysql.service

metadata.startup-script:
CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      mkdir -p /home/consul/data
      mkdir -p /home/consul/consul.d
      cp /home/packer/nginx.json /home/consul/consul.d/nginx.json
      consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -enable-script-checks -data-dir=/home/consul/data -config-dir=/home/consul/consul.d > /dev/null 2>&1 &

export VAULT_LICENSE_PATH=/home/packer/vault.hclic
        CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
        mkdir -p /home/consul/data
        consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data  > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
        cd /home/packer
        mkdir data
        gcloud auth list
        echo -e '\n\nseal "gcpckms" {\n  project     = "hc-60eae5ab12e1435dbc20bad03e7"\n  region      = "global"\n  key_ring    = "vault-unseal-dev"\n  crypto_key  = "vault-unseal-dev"\n}'>>  ./vault-config.hcl
        export VAULT_API_ADDR="http://$(gcloud compute instances describe vault-server-1-dev --zone=europe-west1-b  --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)'):8200"
        export VAULT_CLUSTER_ADDR="http://$(gcloud compute instances describe vault-server-1-dev --zone=europe-west1-b  --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)'):8201"
        ./vault server -config=./vault-config.hcl &
        sudo mv ./vault /usr/local/bin
        export VAULT_ADDR=http://127.0.0.1:8200
        echo VAULT_ADDR=$VAULT_ADDR >> /etc/environment
        sleep 15
        vault operator init > init.txt
        SEVENTH_LINE=$(cat init.txt | head -n 7 | tail -n 1)
        export VAULT_TOKEN=$(echo "$SEVENTH_LINE" | awk '{ print $4; }')
        echo VAULT_TOKEN=$VAULT_TOKEN >> /etc/environment
        sleep 10 
        vault login $VAULT_TOKEN
        sleep 10
        vault secrets enable kv
        vault secrets enable gcp
        vault secrets enable database
        vault write -f sys/replication/dr/primary/enable
        vault write sys/replication/dr/primary/secondary-token id="secondary" > sec_token_out.txt
        echo $(cat sec_token_out.txt | head -n 3 | tail -n 1 | awk '{ print $2; }') > sec_token.txt
        sleep 15
        sudo chmod 766 /home/packer/sec_token.txt
        gcloud compute scp --zone="europe-west1-c" /home/packer/sec_token.txt franco_camba@vault-server-2-dev:/home/packer
        gcloud compute project-info add-metadata --metadata=vault-server1-token="$(cat init.txt | head -n 7 | tail -n 1 | awk '{print $4;}')"

export VAULT_LICENSE_PATH=/home/packer/vault.hclic
        CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
        mkdir -p /home/consul/data
        consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data  > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
        cd /home/packer
        mkdir data
        echo -e '\n\nseal "gcpckms" {\n  project     = "hc-60eae5ab12e1435dbc20bad03e7"\n  region      = "global"\n  key_ring    = "vault-unseal-dev"\n  crypto_key  = "vault-unseal-dev"\n}'>>  ./vault-config.hcl
        export VAULT_API_ADDR="http://$(gcloud compute instances describe vault-server-2-dev --zone=europe-west1-c  --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)'):8200"
        export VAULT_CLUSTER_ADDR="http://$(gcloud compute instances describe vault-server-2-dev --zone=europe-west1-c  --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)'):8201"
        ./vault server -config=./vault-config.hcl &
        sudo mv ./vault /usr/local/bin
        export VAULT_ADDR=http://127.0.0.1:8200
        echo VAULT_ADDR=$VAULT_ADDR >> /etc/environment
        sleep 15
        vault operator init > init.txt
        SEVENTH_LINE=$(cat init.txt | head -n 7 | tail -n 1)
        export VAULT_TOKEN=$(echo "$SEVENTH_LINE" | awk '{ print $4; }')
        echo VAULT_TOKEN=$VAULT_TOKEN >> /etc/environment
        sleep 10
        vault login $VAULT_TOKEN
        sleep 10
        sudo chmod 777 /home/packer
        gcloud compute project-info add-metadata --metadata=vault-server2-token="$(cat init.txt | head -n 7 | tail -n 1 | awk '{print $4;}')"
        sleep 60
        vault write sys/replication/dr/secondary/enable token="$(cat /home/packer/sec_token.txt)"

      BOUNDARY_IP=$(gcloud compute instances describe boundary-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      mkdir -p /home/consul/data
      consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data -bind=$BOUNDARY_IP > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
      sudo mkdir /home/packer | cd /home/packer
      sudo touch init.txt
      IP_ADDR=$(gcloud compute instances describe boundary-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].accessConfigs[0].natIP)')
      sudo boundary dev  -api-listen-address 0.0.0.0:9200  -cluster-listen-address 0.0.0.0:9201 -proxy-listen-address=0.0.0.0:9202 -worker-public-address=$IP_ADDR > /dev/null 2>&1 &

CONSUL_ADDR_INT=$(gcloud compute instances describe consul-server-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      MYSQL_IP=$(gcloud compute instances describe mysql-db-dev --zone=europe-west1-b --format='get(networkInterfaces[0].networkIP)')
      mkdir -p /home/consul/data
      consul agent -join=$CONSUL_ADDR_INT -data-dir=/home/consul/data -bind=$MYSQL_IP > /dev/null 2>&1 & 
      sudo systemctl start mysql.service
